{"tid":616380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消波塊減海浪沖擊力","createTime":"2018-04-04T06:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T06:48:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c51dfdf9c2fd929080ab02ce5c2d115f3fd25b53","tid":616380,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T06:48:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180404/20351757\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180404%2F20351757&d=t8u6QFCGTk6vl1kybkTBg9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a7853bda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180404%2F20351757&h=87f55fe9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180404/20351757</a><br />\n<br />\n消波塊減海浪沖擊力<br />\n<br />\n頭條   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180404/large/a0206a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180404%2Flarge%2Fa0206a.gif&h=20c66074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n防波堤的消波塊以混凝土塊製成，並以鋼筋加固，每塊重量可達2公噸。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【話你知】<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋一個人工島的防波堤出現消波塊（Tetrapods）被沖散情況，這些消波塊是巨型的混凝土塊，並以鋼筋加固，普遍為不規則形狀，如四角空心錐體、工字形等，以英泥固定及連結圍着堤壩，一般每塊重量可達1.5至2公噸，尺寸可達2米乘2米。當海浪拍打堤壩時，消波塊之間的空隙便可消耗波浪部份能量，減低波浪拍打的威力，從而減少堤壩受海浪沖擊的壓力。香港萬宜水庫於上世紀70年代興建時，向海的東壩便採用工字形消波塊設計。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李晟謙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t非浚挖式填海較快但風險大<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t大橋醜聞多　議員促交代<br />\n頭條 5小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t通車在即　港珠澳橋人工島　防波堤逾千石躉崩散專家：恐沉降影響隧道結構<br />\n頭條 5小時前"}]}